This product interoperates with CBOMkit and uses a similar repository-scan input
model, including fields such as Git URL and scan path. No CBOMkit frontend
source code was copied into this product.

The Rego policy-evaluation flow is an independently implemented approach
inspired by CBOMkit's use of policy evaluation.

The Docker Compose configuration was copied from CBOMkit and modified for this
project. The applicable CBOMkit notice has been preserved in docker-compose.yml.

This product uses Open Policy Agent and Rego for policy evaluation, and uses
Semgrep-compatible rules for source-code analysis. These product and project
names are used only to describe interoperability and do not imply endorsement.

See THIRD_PARTY_NOTICES.md for additional attribution and dependency notes.
